profile:
Improve the health of your trees and beautify your property with Taplin’s Tree Care, a family-owned operation based in Orillia. Available 24 hours for emergency storm work, we are certified arborists specializing in tree pruning, cabling, bracing, stump grinding, removal and site clearing.

Rotten old trees can be hazardous if not removed in time. That is why Taplin’s Tree Care provides you reliable tree removal services in the Orillia area.

We specialize in various tree removal services such as:

Branch cleaning
Leaves cleanup
Strump grinding
Roots removal
And much more

Contact us to today for more information about our services and for pricing. We will be happy to assist you.

profile: Davey has been Canada's professional tree service since 1880. From the GTA to Vancouver, we help residential, commercial and municipal clients care for their trees and shrubs and manage their green assets. As Consumer Choice Award recipient for Business Excellence in many markets, we understand the value of great client service. Our arborists live in the communities we serve and as employee owners, share the company's success locally. Whether our arborists are helping a family in Victoria care for their favourite tree, providing Hydro in Calgary with storm response mobilization and post-storm support, assessing and maintaining the trees at a community park in Ottawa or providing an arborist report for a municipality in the GTA, our commitment to delivering the highest quality tree service and urban forestry consulting remains the same.
